    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "広報さん、答えて下さいよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ PR‚ answer our questions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.7666666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "朝倉さんの次の社長は誰なんですかー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who is going to take Asakura-san’s place as the next president?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "所属アイドルのマネジメントに今後影響が出ると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get the feeling this will negatively impact the management of the idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思うのですが？　どうお考えですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "signed here. What do you think about that?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.600000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "テレビでは見たけど\nすごい数のマスコミね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s one thing seeing it on TV‚\nbut there really are a lot of reporters here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "とても正面からは入れないな……やっぱり天動さんは\n置いてきて良かった。とても彼女には見せられない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way we can enter from the front door.\nI’m glad we left Tendo-san behind. I don’t want her to see this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.24491096678235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 27.51157770156861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "業者専用の裏口があるの\n多分、そこならマスコミも手薄なはずよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a backdoor for staff.\nThe reporters probably haven’t found it yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.811577701568606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "マスコミがいたら俺が間に入ります\n早く中に入って、みんなとコンタクトを取りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they have‚ I’ll stand between you and them.\nLet’s get inside as quickly as possible and make contact with the girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.444911034901935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 38.4115777015686
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、助かるわ\n……葵達が心配ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. That’s a big help.\nI’m worried about Aoi and the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 43.6782443682
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 43.6782443682
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 44.04491103490193
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 47.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、バンプロダクションです！\nいえ、私は所属アイドルで経営のことはちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Van Productions here!\nUh‚ I’m just an idol signed here. I don’t know the business side of things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 51.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "愛、そんな体たらくでどうするの？\n一流のアイドルには経営者目線も必要らしいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ how can you keep yourself in such a state?\nTop idols need to also be business-savvy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.61157770156863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 59.61157770156863
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 64.8782443682353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、アイドルって勉強することが多過ぎます……\n葵さ～ん、どうしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ oh… Idols have way too many things to study.\nAoi-san~! What shall we do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.8782443682353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、電話なんて出なくていいよ……\nはぁ、面倒だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys don’t have to answer the phone.\n*sigh* What a drag.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.11157770156862,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3155.0889650980453,
          "startTime": 74.26666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.3333333333258,
          "startTime": 73.74491103490195
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.26495987451995
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "葵！　愛！　こころ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi! Ai! Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、莉央。それに君か、久しぶりだね\n社長就任おめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Rio. And you‚ too. Long time no see.\nCongrats on becoming president.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.18248815414233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 83.98248815414235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺は社長じゃ――いや、今はそんなことはいい\nここにいるのは君達だけか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not the pres—never mind‚ that’s not important.\nAre you girls the only ones here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.91582148747568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 91.349154820809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そうみたいだね\n偉い人はみんな、警察らしいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like it.\nAll the grownups are with the cops right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.61582148747564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 96.38248815414231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん！　電話がひっきりなしにかかってきて\n大変なんです！　手伝って下さい～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san! The phone just keeps ringing and ringing‚\nand we don’t know what to do! Please helllp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.31582148747567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 102.48248815414233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "先輩方、もう訴えちゃいましょ～！\nこの扱いを労働基準なんちゃらに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dear senpais‚ I propose we sue!\nReport our ill-treatment to the Labor Law blah blah blah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.43333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……愛、まずは受話器を置きなさい\nそれは私達の仕事じゃないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai… let’s start by hanging up the phone.\nThat’s not our job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.38248815414232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 114.84915482080899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、は、はい！　すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! R-right! Sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.849154820809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、姫野さんに会いたいんだ\n心当たりはない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ I want to see Himeno-san.\nDo you know where she might be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.58248815414228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 123.3491548208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、えっとあなたは\nどこかでお見かけしたことが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! I think\nI’ve seen you somewhere before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.46666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 127.84915482080896
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 127.84915482080896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "私、思い出しました～！\n星見プロの冴えないマネージャーさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! I remember!\nHoshimi Productions’ boring manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.31582148747566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
